---
title: Sweet Soy Tofu & Ponzu Slaw with Sesame Kumara Fries & Mayo
description: This tofu has layers upon layers of flavour, first being cooked in our staple sweet-soy seasoning, then being tossed in sweet chilli! Sesame-crusted kumara fries and a crunchy, zingy slaw act as the perfect side-kicks to this superstar dish.
